name: OCKOutcomeQuery
desc: A query that limits which outcomes the store returns, when you are fetching.

items.name: init(for: Date)
items.desc: Creates an outcome query with a specific date.

items.name: init(dateInterval: DateInterval)
items.desc: Creates an outcome query with a specific date interval.

items.name: init(OCKAnyOutcomeQuery)
items.desc: Creates an outcome query with a specific query.

items.name: var taskIDs: [String]
items.desc: An array of task identifiers you can use to match outcomes in the query-returned results.

items.name: var taskVersionIDs: [OCKLocalVersionID]
items.desc: An array of task version identifiers you can use to match outcomes in the query-returned results.

items.name: var taskRemoteIDs: [String]
items.desc: An array of task remote identifiers you can use to match outcomes in the query-returned results.

items.name: var limit: Int?
items.desc: The maximum number of results the query returns.

items.name: var dateInterval: DateInterval?
items.desc: A date interval for entities that match the query.

items.name: var groupIdentifiers: [String]
items.desc: An array of group identifers that match the query.

items.name: var ids: [String]
items.desc: An array of unique identifiers that belong to the entities that match the query.

items.name: var localIDs: [OCKLocalVersionID]
items.desc: An array of version identifiers to limit the query results by.

items.name: var offset: Int
items.desc: An integer value that indicates how much to offset the query results, and which can be used to paginate results.

items.name: var remoteIDs: [String]
items.desc: An array of remote IDs for entities that match the query.

items.name: var tags: [String]
items.desc: An array of tags by which to limit the query results.

items.name: var sortDescriptors: [OCKOutcomeSortDescriptor]
items.desc: The order in which you want to sort the query results.

items.name: enum OCKOutcomeSortDescriptor
items.desc: The values that indicate how you want to sort queried outcomes.
